data.name: Commercial Data Storage
data.description:
Commercial Data Storage is short for CDS, claims to be a protocol based on POTS (Proof of Traffic-Measured Storage) traffic storage consensus technology and focuses on financial traffic storage, and is committed to realizing trust, security, efficient problem solving and promotion of financial business development in financial transactions. CDS' design is claimed to combine the well-known distributed technology concept of IPFS, and take into account the special needs of financial data flow, and finally determine the building of POTS-based flow storage consensus technology.
